'''Nova Starlight''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female's]] [[Perfume/Legends|perfume]] with a very sweet fragrance. It came in a disk-shaped container with a button in the middle that would spray the fragrance when pressed.

[[Sariss]] and [[Nikki Idd]] were both known to have used it.

